{"tid":1010010,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲禮物唔送好過送","createTime":"2019-02-05T15:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T15:51:33.000Z","uid":184005,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8006efe61a581f33a840df726cf6105f687dd48f","tid":1010010,"uid":184005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T15:21:48.000Z","msg":"事關男朋友成撚日送埋啲假野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如波鞋 飾物 袋<br />\n收到我就扮開心，但一睇就知假野黎<br />\n扮野問佢邊到買，佢話上網買<br />\n唔知佢係比人呃定貪平野<br />\n同佢講又驚傷佢自尊<br />\n波鞋依家野，真係冇辦法着假嘅岀街<br />\n唯有自己走去買返對真嘅頂擋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有成日收淘寶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78e3c71194c002fc6c5050567da863f93baa3f9","tid":1010010,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T15:24:00.000Z","msg":"分手啦<br />\n送假野呃你<br />\n搵個有$架啦"},{"pid":"70573a87364270e9d36695cad352e4e1fdd9ff32","tid":1010010,"uid":47590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T15:28:28.000Z","msg":"不如同佢講折現啦<br />\n你可以買自己鍾意既野之餘又唔怕收到假野<br />\n好過佢咁鬼鍾意買假野送俾你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66f38fc2a85f93356101066ca1e877769816a58","tid":1010010,"uid":19194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T15:47:33.000Z","msg":"買左但唔啱自己用又係難搞，留低用唔著，又唔可以同佢講唔啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630de7664a56b36aada9372a0133389040e9a594","tid":1010010,"uid":161126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T15:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57ce382608ac6c9e15bfa1ce98d7c56a1fa7a2a","tid":1010010,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"男女朋友，有咩咪直接講囉"}]}